#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "CIVILIAN POWER ARMOR"
msgstr "民用動力裝甲"

#. ~ Description for CIVILIAN POWER ARMOR
#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "Adds a few power armor items"
msgstr "新增幾件動力裝甲物品"

#: .\power_armor.json
msgid "Commercial Depowered armor"
msgid_plural "Commercial Depowered armors"
msgstr[0] "商用無動力裝甲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Commercial Depowered armor'}
#: .\power_armor.json
msgid ""
"The DoubleTech civilian Power Armor,: A heavy suit of basic power armor that"
" has been modified for civilian use, And Has Been Made For Storage, This "
"suit has had its servos and cooling system stripped out, meaning it no "
"longer requires power."
msgstr "雙科民用動力裝甲：一套經過民用改裝的重型基礎動力裝甲，專為儲存設計。該裝甲的伺服系統和冷卻系統已被移除，意味著不再需要動力。"

#: .\power_armor.json
msgid "Commercial power armor"
msgid_plural "Commercial power armors"
msgstr[0] "商用動力裝甲"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'Commercial power armor'}.
#: .\power_armor.json
msgid "The %s engages."
msgstr "%s啟動。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Commercial power armor'}
#: .\power_armor.json
msgid ""
"A suit of DoubleTech Power Armor, Mk. I-C.  This model Is Made For "
"Commercial Use, This Model Was Very Common To See On Rich Members Of "
"society. Like all DoubleTech power armor, the control and climate-regulation"
" systems require direct skin contact."
msgstr ""
"一套雙科動力裝甲，Mk. I-C型。此型號專為商業用途製造，曾常見於社會富裕階層。與所有雙科動力裝甲一樣，其控制和氣候調節系統需要直接皮膚接觸。"

#: .\power_armor.json
msgid "Commercial power armor (active)"
msgid_plural "Commercial power armors (active)"
msgstr[0] "商用動力裝甲（激活狀態）"

#. ~ Use action menu_text for {'str': 'Commercial power armor (active)',
#. 'str_pl': 'Commercial power armors (active)'}.
#: .\power_armor.json
msgid "Turn off"
msgstr "關閉"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'Commercial power armor (active)', 'str_pl':
#. 'Commercial power armors (active)'}.
#: .\power_armor.json
msgid "The %s disengages."
msgstr "%s關閉。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Commercial power armor (active)', 'str_pl':
#. 'Commercial power armors (active)'}
#: .\power_armor.json
msgid ""
"A suit of DoubleTech Power Armor, Mk. I-C.  This model Is Made For "
"Commercial Use, This Model Was Very Common To See On Rich Members Of "
"society. Like all DoubleTech power armor, the control and climate-regulation"
" systems require direct skin contact.  It is currently turned on, activate "
"it to turn it off."
msgstr ""
"一套雙科動力裝甲，Mk. "
"I-C型。此型號專為商業用途製造，曾常見於社會富裕階層。與所有雙科動力裝甲一樣，其控制和氣候調節系統需要直接皮膚接觸。當前為開啟狀態，激活以關閉。"
